{
  "stem": "3631.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the police picked us up, they did not tell us anything about any deportation procedure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just told you, we have to come to the police quarters to-- and then they talk to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our, our passports or papers were invalidated when we got to that hall where they all assembled at.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when they said, well, if you want to go home to pick up a suitcase, you, you can do that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and that was about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after we came to Poland, if I remember right, they asked for-- they said you can ask for permission for one in the family to go back for three days to Germany to liquidate things.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did not do this, because we did not want to separate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, our aunt packed up some of our belongings, even if I remember right, shipped some of our furniture to, to Poland-- which, which we got after a month or a couple of months-- and shipped some clothes.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she more or less liquidated our apartment and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but not the business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened to the business-- it was just closed up, and--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Jetti, J-E-T-T-I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her married name was Kohn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kohn is-- I think it was K-O-H-N, I'm not sure, or C-O-H-N, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she lived in Cologne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an older sister of my father's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her husband had died a year before that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we, we were driven in large transporter, like two police transporter, open ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to sit in 10 rows of five, six people each.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were driven through the whole city, and the people stood, of course, and, and looking what, what, what was going on.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
